        <headline>Special Weather Statement issued August 3 at 1:39PM PDT by NWS Pendleton OR</headline>
        <description>At 138 PM PDT, Doppler radar was tracking a strong thunderstorm over
Brothers, or 37 miles south of Prineville, moving northeast at 20
mph.

HAZARD...Half inch hail.

SOURCE...Radar indicated.

IMPACT...Minor hail damage to vegetation is possible.

Locations impacted include...
Brothers.
</description>
        <instruction>If outdoors, consider seeking shelter inside a building.</instruction>
